Package: rstep
Type: Package
Title: rstep: a workflow for STEP (Sahelian Transpiration Evaporation and Productivity) model under R
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yelognisse Agbohessou <ayulrich@yahoo.fr>
Maintainer: Yelognisse Agbohessou <ayulrich@yahoo.fr>
Year: 2022
Description: rstep provides simple functions to run STEP and automatize the different tasks when performing 1D and/or 2D STEP (Mougin et al. 1995) simulation. 
